{"tid":1695152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澤叻大戰既結論：對話係冇用，因為藍絲係唔會認自己錯","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:37:02.000Z","uid":34869,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"89fdcb35958e68dea60ce37db7f7cc63911b3080","tid":1695152,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"之前仲有人幻想對話可以解決問題<br />\n今日荷蘭叻既表現就話比你知根本冇可能<br />\n因為藍殘一群唔係用事實黎分對錯，係用「我啱你錯」既心態去思考<br />\n總之我最正確，你睇到既野我都睇唔到, 我唔知, 我唔理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總之我最正確</span><br />\n<br />\n同班差佬一樣, 總之我地3萬既隻綠曱由就一定啱，你地講咩都錯，行出街都錯<br />\n左膠和理非們唔該認清事實，呢班藍殘係冇撚得救"},{"pid":"73a96314aedea60d7a83828bffa4610ec34d6823","tid":1695152,"uid":34869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"唔好最妄想可以感化到藍殘"},{"pid":"6763e4652ab07089b7f190b8a63155693f6bc201","tid":1695152,"uid":150610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"不因惡人而影響做法，不因惡人而懲罰好人<br />\n有啲人係衰on9衰無知衰吸收資訊能力<br />\n對唔對話係選擇，但選擇不受限於極惡"},{"pid":"54e842fa28156a8571d550fe836f7c09535d14ad","tid":1695152,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3712a856b7b3c2147f6456708fc0bfc77b092d35","tid":1695152,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"佢都仲話721係互毆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7b5af2a6ad5155588893d952d176c4f29e8acb","tid":1695152,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"將警暴帶入區 親身見過受過咪知囉"},{"pid":"17745d5cda06254f9263f1398cc650b8af7da8c7","tid":1695152,"uid":64882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"如果"},{"pid":"b971b0b37587cf1bd2da530d1cb35e85897993ba","tid":1695152,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73a96314aedea60d7a83828bffa4610ec34d6823","tid":16